Chain Shirt.COPY=Raiment of Chains				TYPE:Magic		SOURCEPAGE:p.12		EQMOD:Special Ability ~ +1 ~ Armor.Special Ability ~ Enhancement Cost|5000													SPROP:The wearer can don or remove the armor as a move action. Three times per day as a standard action, the wearer can command chains to shoot out from the raiment of chains and attempt a reposition or trip combat maneuver check against a single target within 20 feet. The wearer is considered proficient with the chains and uses her own CMB with a +1 enhancement bonus on the check. The combat maneuver provokes attacks of opportunity as normal. The chains immediately retract back into the armor once the combat maneuver check has been attempted.
